comment: Payton (ORL) makes incidental contact with Collison (SAC) that does not affect his SQBR.
[Observable in enhanced video] Temple (SAC) moves his pivot foot.
Fournier (ORL) legally contests Temple's (SAC) jump shot attempt.
Cauley-Stein (SAC) maintains legal guarding position and makes incidental contact with Vucevic (ORL) that does not affect his post move and shot attempt.
Collison (SAC) makes marginal contact with Payton (ORL) that does not affect his ability to defend the play.
Temple (SAC) and Fournier (ORL) briefly engage and separate prior to the inbound pass.
Vucevic (ORL) commits a take foul on Collison (SAC).
Payton (ORL) grabs Collison's (SAC) jersey and affects his FOM prior to the inbound pass.
Ross (ORL) maintains legal guarding position and makes incidental contact with Hield (SAC) that does not affect his shot attempt.
Vucevic (ORL) extends his arms into Temple (SAC) when he sets the screen.
Temple (SAC) grabs Vucevic's (ORL) jersey as he attempts to avoid the screen.
Vucevic (ORL) sets the screen on Temple (SAC) and absorbs the contact.
Temple (SAC) is in a legal guarding position and deflects the ball away from Vucevic (ORL).
Gordon (ORL) commits a take foul on Collison (SAC).
